					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11958151#post-4263313</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11958151/scp-4366#post-4263313</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2019 13:50:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RJB_R</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1229263</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like that there’s&#8230; something happening here but we don’t know what. That can be a tough tightrope walk but it’s managed here fairly well. I also think the birds as described are cute and I wanna be their friend. I don’t think that the bird camouflage and the other elements of the article come together quite as well as they could, honestly each section feels like it could’ve been from an entirely different article, but it still works. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11958151#post-4261341</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11958151/scp-4366#post-4261341</link>
				<description></description>
