				<wikidot:authorName>Connor MacWarren</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3741977</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Humans can't completely decipher the sound. It's a lot similar to the phenomenon of when the pressure in the air changes and you can sort of hear a hum of sorts. This is the closest they have to a description of the noise that it makes.</p> 
				 	]]>
